@using FluentUI.Demo.Shared.Pages.MenuBar.Examples

<h1>MenuBar</h1>

<p>
    A horizontal menu bar component that integrates seamlessly with Fluent UI styling and theming.
    The MenuBar provides a flexible navigation solution for applications with support for flat menu items,
    dropdown menus, navigation links, and custom content areas.
</p>

<p>
    Key features include:
    <ul>
        <li>Support for flat menu items and hierarchical dropdown menus</li>
        <li>Navigation links with href support</li>
        <li>Click handlers and event callbacks</li>
        <li>Disabled and selected states</li>
        <li>Custom content areas for search boxes, user profiles, etc.</li>
        <li>Multiple appearance styles (Stealth, Accent, Outline, etc.)</li>
        <li>Responsive design with mobile-friendly layout</li>
        <li>Full integration with Fluent UI design tokens</li>
        <li>Accessibility support with proper ARIA roles</li>
    </ul>
</p>

